  <brief_title>Tradipitant in Treatment-resistant Pruritus Associated With Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of Tradipitant in Treatment-resistant Pruritus Associated With Atopic Dermatitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
