  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study to be conducted in
      the United States in subjects with treatment-resistant pruritus diagnosed with atopic
      dermatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
